ct Function & Corporate Cynicism V.O.: The Desperation Candle doesn't summon divine intervention, kid. It burns for exactly 17 weeks—the length of a regular season—and then it flares out, perfectly synchronised with the moment your team is mathematically eliminated. V.O.: It manages your expectations. It ensures a clean break. (SHOT: CHRIS lights the pathetic candle. The screen shows the final play: interception. CHRIS sighs, but the candle is already extinguishing itself.) Call to Action (1:45 – 2:00) V.O. (Harsh, Final): Don't waste your energy on actual hope. V.O.: LORD ITS ME AGAIN is the only product that respects the dark, undeniable truth of your team's mediocrity. It's not about winning. It's about efficiently processing the loss. V.O.: Stop wasting time. Use the $20 you were going to spend on a new hat and invest in LORD ITS ME AGAIN. Because we both know you're going to be back here next year. We’re counting on it. (SCENE END) Auto Prompt Reflection Kling V2.6 Pro Auto-select Models Image to Video 9:16 3 ~ 5s Options 1/1"}]},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"text":"Source: "},{"type":"link","href":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=c650f268-f951-49d3-92de-8d5837a8e336","children":[{"text":"https://www.genspark.ai/agents?id=c650f268-f951-49d3-92de-8d5837a8e336"}]}]}]
